001100*     --- REFORMAT VERIFIED RECEIPTS POST FILE ---              * 00110000
001200*                                                               * 00120000
001300*    THE PURPOSE OF THIS PROGRAM IS TO CONVERT THE VERIFIED     * 00130000
001310*    RECEIPTS RECORDS TO A NEW FORMAT, AND CREATE A SEPARATE    * 00131000
001320*    RECORD FOR THE LOAD PORTION OF THE VERIFIED RECEIPTS THAT  * 00132000
001330*    CONTAIN A DOMESTIC PRIVATE LABEL LOAD AMOUNT.  THIS        * 00133000
001340*    SEPARATE RECORD WILL ALLOW THE LOAD AMOUNT TO BE POSTED TO * 00134000
001350*    A SEPARATE GL ACCOUNT.                                     * 00135000
001360*---------------------------------------------------------------* 00136000
001370* DB2 TABLES:                                                   * 00137000
001380*  1. PURCHASE ORDER HEADER            (TPURCHS)                * 00138000
001390*                                                               * 00139000
001400* INPUT:                                                        * 00140000
001500*  1. STORE EXTRACT FILE, SUMMED BY    (STOREEXT)               * 00150000
001600*     PO AND LOCATION.                                          * 00160000
001700*                                                               * 00170000
001800* OUTPUT:                                                       * 00180000
001900*  1. GL VERIFIED RECEIPT POST FILE.   (APRD006)                * 00190000
002000*                                                               * 00200000
002100*---------------------------------------------------------------* 00210000
002200*   CHANGES:                                                    * 00220000
002300*    DATE  02/04/2008                                           * 00230000
002400*        CHANGE MADE: INITIAL IMPLEMENTATION.                   * 00240000
002500*        MADE BY: CHRISTINE TWIEHAUS      WR/IR #: WR32664      * 00250000
002600*                                                               * 00260000
002700*    DATE  02/11/2008                                           * 00270000
002800*        CHANGE MADE: ADDED STANDARD SQL MESSAGE DISPLAYS SO    * 00280000
002900*        SUPPORT PERSON COULD DETERMINE THE CAUSE OF THE ABEND. * 00290000
003000*        MADE BY: NANCY EILBES            WR/IR #: P000255227   * 00300000
003100*                                                               * 00310000
003200*    DATE  06/27/2008                                           * 00320000
003300*    CHANGE MADE: MODIFIED LOGIC THAT WAS CONTROLLING WHETHER TO* 00330000
003400*    CREATE A LOAD RECORD TO COMPARE EXTENDED COST AND 1ST COST * 00340000
003500*    AS UNEQUAL RATHER THAN EXTENDED COST GREATER THAN 1ST COST.* 00350000
003600*    IN THE CASE OF AN ADJUSTMENT WITH NEGATIVE AMOUNTS, THE    * 00360000
003700*    EXTENDED COST WAS LESS THAN THE FIRST COST SO NO LOAD WAS  * 00370000
003800*    CREATED, EVEN THOUGH IT SHOULD HAVE BEEN.                  * 00380000
003900*    MADE BY: NANCY EILBES            WR/IR #: INC000000417637  * 00390000
004000*                                                               * 00400000
004100*DATE  08/26/2014                                                *00410000
004200*    CHANGE MADE: MODIFIED LOGIC IN B200-PROCESS-RECEIPTS THAT   *00420000
004300*    USES PO TYPE TO DETERMINE WHICH COST FIELD TO USE TO REMOVE *00430000
004400*    PO TYPE CD FROM THE PATH USING UNIT COST SO IT WILL NOW USE *00440000
004500*    FIRST COST.  THIS CHANGE WILL CORRECT A BALANCING ISSUE THAT*00450000
004600*    HAS BEEN OCCURRING SINCE RMS13 WENT LIVE WITH ITS DIFFERENT *00460000
004700*    RULES ON MAINTAINING UNIT COST.                             *00470000
004800*    MADE BY: NANCY EILBES            WR/IR #: CHG0090736        *00480000
004900*                                                                *00490000
004910*DATE  10/07/2019                                                *00491000
004920*    CHANGE MADE: RENAMED GLKUT015 TO APKUT002.  COPYBOOK        *00492000
004930*    GLRD005 WAS RENAMED APRD006.  ALL LOGIC REMAINED THE SAME.  *00493000
004980*    MADE BY: NANCY EILBES            WR/IR #: CHG0233628        *00498000
004990*                                                                *00499000
004991*DATE  10/06/2021                                                *00499105
004992*    CHANGE MADE: MODIFIED LOGIC IN B200-PROCESS-RECEIPTS TO     *00499204
004993*    INCLUDE EXCLUSIVE BRAND POS (PURCHS-DERVD-LBL-TYP-CDE = 'E')*00499304
004994*    IN THE LOGIC TO CREATE THE PD LOAD RECORDS.                 *00499404
004996*    MADE BY: NANCY EILBES            WR/IR #: CHG0262261        *00499605
